<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>The virtual table read of Fast Times at Ridgemont High is happening on Thursday night.</p>

<p>And so star-studded is the cast for the charitable event, that even Chrissy Teigen appeared starstruck when she dropped into husband John Legend's Zoom call with his fellow performers.</p>

<p>The former Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issue covergirl was greeted by A-listers like Brad Pitt, Jennifer Aniston, Julia Roberts, Matthew McConaughey and Morgan Freeman during her cameo in a teaser trailer for the event. </p>

<p>OMG: So star-studded is the cast for the Fast Times at Ridgemont High virtual table read, that even Chrissy Teigen appeared starstruck when she dropped into husband John Legend's Zoom call with his fellow performers</p>

<p>As her EGOT-winning spouse introduced his fellow actors, an increasingly-flustered Teigen could be heard to utter 'Oh my god!' and 'What the heck?!'</p>

<p>Also appearing on the conference call were Henry Golding, Jimmy Kimmel, Shia LaBeouf, Ray Liotta, and Sean Penn, as well as host Dane Cook. </p>

<p>As he wrapped up the extensive cast list, Chrissy excused herself from the proceedings, telling the impressive performers, 'Sorry, bye!' </p>

<p>She then ducked off camera, making herself scarce. </p>

<p>Starstruck: As her EGOT-winning spouse introduced his fellow actors, an increasingly-flustered Teigen could be heard to utter 'Oh my god!' and 'What the heck?!'</p>

